{"tid":1548090,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"機場特別交通消息","createTime":"2019-09-07T02:06:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-07T03:03:22.000Z","uid":213167,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"77384047b88f9447a2b7b15b9f6bbb5eab252fec","tid":1548090,"uid":213167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T02:06:34.000Z","msg":"7/9【#特別交通消息】因應運輸處同機管局指示，以配合機場實施進出管制措施，往返香港國際機場同北大嶼山嘅交通服務會作出調整：<br />\n<br />\n1.港鐵旗下機場快綫：<br />\n&bull; 列車服務只維持來往機場至香港站，每10分鐘一班；<br />\n&bull; 列車唔停九龍、青衣、博覽館站；<br />\n&bull; 博覽館站暫時關閉。<br />\n&bull; 九龍站嘅市區預辦登機服務暫停，而香港站嘅市區預辦登機服務，繼續維持喺航班起飛前90分鐘截止。<br />\n<br />\n2.機場/北大嶼山對外巴士：<br />\n「應運輸署要求」<br />\n&bull; 由上晝十點半開始，由新界開出嘅E線班次改停東涌東堤灣畔；<br />\n&bull; 由上晝十一點開始，S1同S64停駛。"},{"pid":"1894cda84c7da2f5a04b433f537b496ce7a05276","tid":1548090,"uid":76702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T02:07:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b09feea44ff412cda73d96363b24375c2077f4fc","tid":1548090,"uid":163502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T02:07:25.000Z","msg":"Fc?"},{"pid":"de85cbb5a74d92fa14e93f5d0253bf4294851ecb","tid":1548090,"uid":213167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b09feea44ff412cda73d96363b24375c2077f4fc","tid":1548090,"uid":163502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T02:07:25.000Z","msg":"Fc?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T02:10:19.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://news.now.com/?refer=Share\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2F%3Frefer%3DShare&d=Lg84ZazuoAMv777FGbMFAXyU4AarvyINc8S1qmu5ZLM%3D&h=99a662de\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2F%3Frefer%3DShare&h=1b16d13d\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.now.com/?refer=Share</a>"},{"pid":"82da972585529ed9deeb73831d7b6bfc7f7de870","tid":1548090,"uid":158404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T02:10:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0b8581d2d41e79d900bbdd463a2b3af229eade54","tid"